               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 3ra-133va)
 -
                     Introduction (fols. 3ra-5vb)
 - Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols.
                     10ra-14va)
 - Maṣḥaf za-wäḍʾat ʾǝm-ʾIyarusalem “Book that Came from
                     Jerusalem” (fols. 14va-20ra)
 - Antiphons (kǝśtat) (fols. 30ra-31va,
                     49rb-49va, 65ra-65va, 67vb-68rb, 74ra-rb, 76rb)
 - Homily by St Jacob of
                     Serug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols. 50va-60ra)
 - Homily by
                     ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols. 60ra-62ra)
 - Lǝfāfa ṣǝdq
                     “Bandlet of Righteousness” (fols. 89va-90va)
 - Mangada samāy “Journey to
                     Heaven” (fols. 93ra-94vb)</summary>
